{"lemma":"ذَرْعُ","slug":"ذَرْعُ","root":"ذ.ر.ع","root_slug":"ذ-ر-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ذ-ر-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"ذَرْع","root":"ذرع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":3},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n13795","n13801","n13796","n13802","n13803"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B0%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%92%D8%B9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n13795","headword_ar":"ذَرْعٌ","root":"*rE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", [inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araEa","text_ar":"ذَرَعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] in its primary acceptation, signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stretching forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extending, the arm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fore leg:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) [or rather, when said of a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fore arm;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and of a beast,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the arm;"},{"kind":"text","text":"though the whole arm of a man is generally stretched forth with his fore arm, and the whole fore leg of a beast with his arm: and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta*oriyEN","text_ar":"تَذْرِيعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_i*oraAEN","text_ar":"اـِذْرَاعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta*ar~uEN","text_ar":"تَذَرُّعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signify the same, as will be shown by explanations of their verbs.] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araEa AlbaEiyru yadahu","text_ar":"ذَرَعَ البَعِيرُ يَدَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camel stretched forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extended, his fore leg"},{"kind":"text","text":"in going: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaEiyru","text_ar":"البَعِيرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t*r~E","text_ar":"تذرّع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The camel stretched forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extended, his arm"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iraAEahu","text_ar":"ذِرَاعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":") in his going. (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araEahu","text_ar":"ذَرَعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aroEN","text_ar":"ذَرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He measured it with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iraAEN","text_ar":"ذِرَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cubit"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Msb, K;) namely, a garment, or piece of cloth, (S, Msb, K,) &c.: (S:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araEahu bi*iraAEihi","text_ar":"ذَرَعَهُ بِذِرَاعِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he measured it with his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*rAE","text_ar":"ذراع"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also 5.] ―         -b3-  You say of a she-camel,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta*oraEu AlfalaApa","text_ar":"تَذْرَعُ الفَلَاةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She goes quickly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swiftly, over the desert, as though measuring it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tu*aAriEuhaA","text_ar":"تُذَارِعُهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buEodaAlT~ariyqi","text_ar":"بُعْدَالطَّرِيقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tu*aAriEu","text_ar":"تُذَارِعُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She stretches forth her fore legs and so traverses the distance of the way."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araEa fulaAnFA","text_ar":"ذَرَعَ فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He strangled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throttled, such a one from behind him with the fore arm;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~Ehu","text_ar":"ذرّعهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) or the latter, inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta*oriyEN","text_ar":"تَذْرِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifies, simply,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he strangled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throttled, him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L;) but more properly,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he put his neck between his fore arm and neck and upper arm, and so strangled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"throttled, him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~E","text_ar":"ذرّع","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, has both of these significations. (L.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araEa","text_ar":"ذَرَعَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaEiyra","text_ar":"البَعِيرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He trod upon the arm"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*rAE","text_ar":"ذراع"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the camel,"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"while the latter was lying with his breast upon the ground and his fore legs folded,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that a person might mount him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araEahu AlqaYo'u","text_ar":"ذَرَعَهُ القَىْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) aor. as above, (Mgh,) and so the inf. n., (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vomit overcame him, and came forth to his mouth before he was aware,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * Mgh, Msb, * K, * TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and issued from him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vomiting came upon him without his intending it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araEa Einodahu","text_ar":"ذَرَعَ عِنْدَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ibn-'Abbád, K,) inf. n. as above, (Ibn-'Abbád,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made intercession with him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K.) [Said in the TA to be tropical; I suppose because the stretching forth the arm is a common action of a person interceding.] You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araEotu lifulaAnK Einoda","text_ar":"ذَرَعْتُ لِفُلَانٍ عِنْدَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amiyri","text_ar":"الاَمِيرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I made intercession for such a one with the prince."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariEa A_ilayohi","text_ar":"ذَرِعَ اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fariHa","text_ar":"فَرِحَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Ibn-'Abbád, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araEN","text_ar":"ذَرَعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TK,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made intercession to him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K.) In the O,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariEa bihi","text_ar":"ذَرِعَ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made intercession"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariEa","text_ar":"ذَرِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drank from a skin"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ziq~","text_ar":"زِقّ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAriEN","text_ar":"ذَارِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariEato rijolaAhu","text_ar":"ذَرِعَتْ رِجْلَاهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His legs became tired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fatigued."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K.)       -A6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*araAEapN","text_ar":"ذَرَاعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. an inf. n., of which the verb is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aruEa","text_ar":"ذَرُعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The being wide in step,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and light,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"active, in pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","Msb","K","Mgh","TK"]},{"entry_id":"n13801","headword_ar":"ذَرْعٌ","root":"*rE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", in its primary acceptation, has the signification explained in the first sentence of this article. (S, TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence, it is used in the sense of] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iraAEN","text_ar":"ذِرَاعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) or a man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reach,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extent of power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And hence the phrases,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAqa biAlA^amori *aroEuhu","text_ar":"ضَاقَ بِالاَمْرِ ذَرْعُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iraAEuhu","text_ar":"ذِرَاعُهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaAqa biAlA^amori *aroEFA","text_ar":"ضَاقَ بِالاَمْرِ ذَرْعًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Msb, K,) in which the last word is in the accus. case as an explicative, for the original form of the phrase is that first mentioned, (TA,) and sometimes they said ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iraAEFA","text_ar":"ذِرَاعًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was unable to do,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accomplish, the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though meaning, he stretched forth his arm to it and it did not reach it; (S, TA; *) or these phrases are thus used because he who is short in the fore arm will not reach that which he who is long therein reaches, nor will the power of the former equal that of the latter; therefore they are proverbially applied to him whose power falls short of the attainment, or accomplishment, of an affair: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he lacked strength,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability, to do,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accomplish, the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair, and found not any way of escape from what was disagreeable therein:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was unable to bear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"endure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"undertake, the thing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) You say also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA liY bihi *aroEN","text_ar":"مَا لِى بِهِ ذَرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*iraAEN","text_ar":"ذِرَاعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I have not power,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability, to do it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kasara *`lika mino *aroEiY","text_ar":"كَسَرَ ذٰلِكَ مِنْ ذَرْعِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That disabled, hindered, prevented,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"withheld, me from doing that which I desired."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiqoSido bi*aroEika","text_ar":"اِقْصِدْ بِذَرْعِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Deal thou gently with thyself; moderate thyself restrain thyself; i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AirobaEo EalaY nafosika","text_ar":"اِرْبَعْ عَلَى نَفْسِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and let not thy soul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"mind, carry thee beyond thy measure"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"extent"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of power"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ability"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboTarotu fulaAnFA *aroEhu","text_ar":"اَبْطَرْتُ فُلَانًا ذَرْعهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I imposed upon such a one more than he was able to do:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aroEN","text_ar":"ذَرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies (assumed tropical:)  the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"body:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and [accord. to IAar]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abaTaraniY *aroEiY","text_ar":"اَبَطَرَنِى ذَرْعِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He wasted my body, and cut off my means of subsistence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) [See also art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bTr","text_ar":"بطر"},{"kind":"text","text":".] You likewise say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHobu Al*~iraAEi","text_ar":"رَحْبُ الذِّرَاعِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al*~aroEi","text_ar":"الذَّرْعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"] (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man having ample strength, and power, and might in war or fight, courage, valour,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prowess."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHobN","text_ar":"رَحْبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaEiyfu Al*~aroEi","text_ar":"ضَعِيفُ الذَّرْعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Impotent."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL.) ―         -b3-  And hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnN xaAliY Al*~aroEi","text_ar":"فُلَانٌ خَالِى الذَّرْعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one has his heart devoid of anxieties,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"solicitudes, and griefs;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because the heart is sometimes one of the seats of power: or it may mean, agreeably with the original signification of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aroEN","text_ar":"ذَرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such a one is free from the causes of occupation which require the stretching forth of the fore arm and extending of the hand."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 131.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN waAsiEN Al*~aroEi","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ وَاسِعٌ الذَّرْعِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al*~iraAEi","text_ar":"الذِّرَاعِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A man large,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"liberal, in disposition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kabura fiY *aroEiY","text_ar":"كَبُرَ فِى ذَرْعِى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Its occurrence,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"befalling, was of great moment, momentous, grievous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distressing, to me."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aroEN","text_ar":"ذَرْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"measure"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naxolapN *aroEu rajalK","text_ar":"نَخْلَةٌ ذَرْعُ رَجَلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A palm-tree of the measure of the stature of a man."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","Msb","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n13796","headword_ar":"ذرّع","root":"*rE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K, &c.,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta*oriyEN","text_ar":"تَذْرِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) see 1, first sentence. ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He spread himself out widely,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Moheet, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and stretched forth his fore arms,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(El-Moheet, L,) in swimming: (El-Moheet, L, K:) said of a man. (El-Moheet, L.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"raised his fore arms;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and particularly, in announcing good tidings or in warning: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an announcer of good tidings)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made a sign with his arm,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hand."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~E fiY Alma$oYi","text_ar":"ذرّع فِى المَشْىِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He moved about his fore arms in walking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"going along."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~E fY Als~aEoYi","text_ar":"ذرّع فى السَّعْىِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L, TA,) in the O and Moheet and K, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fYAls~aqoYi","text_ar":"فىالسَّقْىِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He helped himself with his arms, and moved them about,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, El-Moheet, L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in walking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walking quickly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"running."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~E liY","text_ar":"ذرّع لِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ayoy^FA mino xabarihi","text_ar":"شَيْيًا مِنْ خَبَرِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acquainted me with somewhat of his tidings,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"case;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) [as though he stretched forth his arm with his information;] said by one who has asked another respecting his case. (TA.) ―         -b6-  [And hence, app.,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~E bika*aA","text_ar":"ذرّع بِكَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acknowledged,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"confessed, such a thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~E fulaAnFA","text_ar":"ذرّع فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~E lahu","text_ar":"ذرّع لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see 1. ―         -b8-  [Hence, perhaps,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~Ehu","text_ar":"ذرّعهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n. as above. (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He killed him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"slew him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~E AlbaEiyra","text_ar":"ذرّع البَعِيرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*r~E lahu","text_ar":"ذرّع لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He bound both of the arms of the camel"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to the shanks"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) and the latter,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"page_break","n":961},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bound the camel with the redundant part of his nose-rein upon his"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the camel's]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arm."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta*oriyEN","text_ar":"تَذْرِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"below.] ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta*oriyEN","text_ar":"تَذْرِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"also signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tinging a captive's fore arm with crocus,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaluwq","text_ar":"خَلُوق"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as a sign of slaughter;"},{"kind":"text","text":"which was done in the time before Mohammad. (Meyd, cited by Freytag.) ―         -b11-  [See also the act. and pass. part. ns., below.]"}],"source_refs":["S","TA","L","K"]},{"entry_id":"n13802","headword_ar":"ذَرَعٌ","root":"*rE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A coveting; desiring eagerly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lusting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K.) [Perhaps an inf. n. of which the verb is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariEa","text_ar":"ذَرِعَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariyEapN","text_ar":"ذَرِيعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n13803","headword_ar":"ذَرِعٌ","root":"*rE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ariyEN","text_ar":"ذَرِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That journeys by night and by day."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Longtongued with evil speech."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)       -A2-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Good in social,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"familiar, intercourse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]}}